        "class": "",
        "text": ". “for all live unto Him” (A.V[167], R.V[168]), is probably an editorial explanatory gloss to make the deep thought of Jesus clearer (not in parallels). The gloss itself needs explanation. Is “all” to be taken without qualification?—",
