        "text": "Romans 14:8-9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Our Lord added, “Ye therefore do greatly err.” But how incomparably less severe is the condemnation of religious and intellectual error, than the burning rebuke against Pharisaic lovelessness !",
